      "updated": 1773640093952,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "etcd distributed database\netcd replica on every control plane node for HA\nin HA env also we need backup and recovery\netcd distributed databases so for write consistency it uses RAFT consensus algorithm.",
