      "updated": 1773640093953,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "K8S work on 3 principles:\n 1. Desired  state :  what you want\n 2. current state  : what you have\n 3. Reconciliation : keeping observed state in sync with desired state (desired = current)\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "K8S work on 3 principles:\n 1. Desired  state :  what you want\n 2. current state  : what you have\n 3. Reconciliation : keeping observed state in sync with desired state (desired = current)\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
