      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773640093953,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Pod is also an atomic operation\nPod is ready when all containers are up and running. \nAll the containers all scheduled in a same node",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Pod is also an atomic operation\nPod is ready when all containers are up and running. \nAll the containers all scheduled in a same node",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "NPyMmuijxf1Oeh2kz3vFd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6200,
      "y": 4780,
      "width": 451,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c0c6",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1462598409,
      "version": 99,
      "versionNonce": 927159734,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773640093953,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Pods are mortal —\n they’re created, they live, and they die\n old pod replaced by new \n    new IP address allocated ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Pods are mortal —\n they’re created, they live, and they die\n old pod replaced by new \n    new IP address allocated ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "opHnDA6YNP4kJzX8yOoYQ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6199.830344306098,
      "y": 4901.122410090281,
      "width": 605,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c0c7",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1083749449,
      "version": 61,
      "versionNonce": 1368295594,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773640093953,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "We can't change the running pod, only can update them. \n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "We can't change the running pod, only can update them. \n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
